Dialogs.Dialog: Did you hear about it, ▲主人公＊▲？
The next training camp was canceled. Suzuki-sensei forgot to submit the application form...
Really？ That's unfair... I was looking forward to stay at Izu Kogen for 2 nights.
We shouldn't blame sensei so much... But yeah, it's a shame.
It was a camping trip were we could stay outside. I was looking forward to it...
Emm, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ You know, I actually won a prize: 2 days 1 night in Atami.
Why don't we go there together？
The thing you said before. Okay...
Do you mean... The travel？ Really？
I see！ I'm sure we can make the best memories there.
Maybe Papa won't forgive me, so I'll keep it secret... if you keep silent about the camp being canceled...
Well, that's not the reason... I want to stay.
Yes... But, I want to be together with you.
I see. Emm, when do you want to go？
If it was on weekend, can you go these days？
Then, we will stay for two days and one night from ▲月▲▲日▲！
You know, I got tickets to travel to Atami again.
Yes, that's why, will you go with me again？
Then, 2 days and 1 night from ▲月▲▲日▲！
(We will travel to Atami together once more, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
Sorry for calling so suddenly. Why don't we go shopping for our travel？
Our travel？ You're right, we need to prepare some things... Okay, let's go！
Yes, shall we go to a shopping mall？
Toiletries for travel... Mostly everyday items. After that, other various things...
(Wait, I'm traveling to the sea in summer...)
I have to buy a swimsuit！
What's wrong？ Did you forget it too？
After this, do we have everything we need？
Yes, it's fine. This makes traveling safe.
I feel like I'm forgetting something.
Then I'll make a list. That way you won't forget anything when checking it, right？
We really should prepare in advance.
Yes... Wait, are you saying I'm not reliable？
Hehe, a little. But during the trip, I think boys are reliable.
Is that so？ I'll do my best. See you.
Good morning, it's a nice day, and it's sunny.
Good morning. I see, I'm glad.
Good morning. It's hot today, do you think it's hotter over there？
Good morning. I wonder about that.
Good morning. Hehe, it's a nice day for traveling, it's a nice weather.
Good morning, it's cold today. Have you been keeping warm？ I hope it won't be cold during our travel.
Good morning. It's going to be okay.
Yes. It's a special trip, so I changed it a little. How do you like it？
Really？ I'm glad I took the plunge.
Really？ I wonder what I should do.
How do you like my clothes today？
Hehe, yay！ I was a little overwhelmed.
(Today's clothes look really good on you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Geez, I wish you were more interested.
Yes... you're right. I should have done something different.
You noticed？ I changed it according to the trip.
It looks so good on you！
Ah... I'm glad. I was thrilled to see if you liked it.
It doesn't change much, huh. Yes, that's fine...
My clothes today... aren't they weird？
(I really like your clothes today, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
They aren't strange, right？ In that case, it's fine.
Ah... There's no time to go back and change clothes...
Yes, it's the travel version, I'm kidding. How do you like it？
Don't lie... No, I wonder what I should do.
How do you like my clothes today？ It suits me？
(I really like your clothes today, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I see... It seems like I've failed.
Hey, do you think there will be wonderful things today？
We must take a transfer here.
Yes. If you change to a limited express here, we will be in Atami soon.
I don't really ride the limited express. Aside from the Shinkansen.
It may be my first time in a train like this.
Yes, we often drive to the airport when I travel with my family.
The transfer was over there. Did you forget？
It really feels like a travel when we're in this train.
I want to enjoy this event together.
By the way, I've always been curious about something...
Didn't you bring a lot of luggage？
Ah, I'm sorry. I asked you to bring mine as well.
That's fine, though. Even though it's two days and one night, what's inside？
Just the normal, right？ Clothes, toiletries, guidebooks, writing items, sewing tools and some medicines.
Is that strange？ Mama said I should be ready for the trip.
Hmmー, I don't know what will happen. If you're prepared for the unknown, everything will be okay, right？
Yes, that's it. If you are prepared, you don't have to worry！ Right？
(It's seems like you're not used to traveling yet, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Ah, no, no. That's not what I... that's not it...
This trip is like our honeymoon... So, I wanted to play the newlyweds... I was just thinking that.
It's embarrassing to be like that.
We are now in our honeymoon！
That's right. Even though we're still high school students, right？
That's right. We can take our time.
We will soon arrive to Atami, we thank you for your continued patronage today.
It's dangerous if you get so excited.
No Papa, Mama or sensei. Just the two of us.
I wonder if something has changed from when we came before.
Now then, where are we going first？
Yes. It's a specialty... but it's a pity...
I won't ever do that to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Even if I marry another person...
Excuse me. Sorry for interrupting but...
I want a picture in front of this statue, so Mr. Boyfriend, can you press the shutter？
Even if no one knows, we look like lovers.
That's right, that much is obvious.
Yes, of course. Hehe！ But, I'm glad we could come here...
Wow, are we going to climb this... How many steps are there？
It's about 600 steps from here. There are more than 800 steps from the bottom.
I'm so sorry. I'm at my limit here, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Only half left. Do your best！
If you climb, you have to go down again. It's impossible...
If you go to the top, the autumn leaves will be beautiful...
Geez, are you lacking exercise？ The name of the Towano Tennis Club will be stained, you know？
Hehe, easy victory？ As expected of the Towano Tennis Club！
Leave it to me！ But, it seems you are still fine, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Nothing like that. I was breathing heavily.
(I didn't see that... You're amazing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
The autumn leaves are beautiful. I can see the city, I'm glad we worked hard.
This shrine is the place where Masako Hojo had a date back in the day.
Then, Minamoto no Yoritomo was here too？ This shrine seems to grant good things.
(I wish my relationship with you develops further, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(Somehow, I feel closer to you than before, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
I hope your wish comes true.
That's right, we didn't eat anything when we arrived here.
I was so absorbed in having fun that I didn't notice it, so let's have lunch.
If you look down, it has a nice view, right？ Let's enter.
(With this view, eating will be fun.)
We can finally take a breather.
Thinking about it, it's a pretty tight schedule.
With 1 night and 2 days, it can't be helped.
Right. Let's do our best after eating！
Then, let's go change our clothes. We'll meet here, okay？
Yes. See you in a few.
(Hmm... If you look around, you're probably the cutest ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Geez, this is kind of weird.
My swimsuit... I think I answered to your request from last time.
(That's right. I wonder if you took countermeasures against sunburn, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Isn't it better to apply sunscreen, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Haha, that's no good. Come here, I'll apply it for you.
Is this sun oil？ I'll get a tan.
Ah, I think you'll look cute with a tan！ I will apply it to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yes, but in this season it doesn't feel like a Sun Beach.
That's right. If it was summer, we could swim in the sea.
Yeah... Should we come back in summer？
Haha, I was thinking the same.
*Phew*... Are you ready to go back？
There are still many places to go.
Right. Then, let's go to the next place.
There are quite a lot of cherry trees in Atami.
Yes, it's beautiful. The cherry blossoms in Atami are blooming very early.
It blooms as much as the cherry trees in Okinawa. That's amazing.
It's so warm. When I hear that, it feels like I'm on a trip elsewhere, even though we're already here.
It looks like my shoes have slipped.
A shoe slip？ Did you bring shoes you're not used to？
We've been walking quite a bit.
Yes, but... it's a special trip... I want to be fashionable.
...You're right, I'm sorry. Please, show me your leg, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yes, thank you. I don't think it's a big deal...
Ah, why don't we go into that store？
Yeah, that's good too. But we have other plans.
But, can we afford to check it？
That's also true... But it's better to go back to the room, together... Right？
Huh？ I don't get it. Shall we go？
It looks like an amusement park, and it seems cool.
The top looks quite nice. It looks a little scary, though...
Let's go quickly. You don't want to be left behind, right？
I get it, I get it.
Oh, it's moving. It's going pretty fast.
Yes, I think we'll get there soon. Hey, can you hold my hand until we get there？
It's fine, but why？ Is it scary after all？
No. It's not that, but can we？
Eh, so that's what it is.
If we put a lock there, we will be forever happy.
Hmm？ A lock, huh. So that's Cape Aijyo.
I wonder if the lock we put here still remains.
I wonder if it was already been taken down. Are you worried about it？
No. After all, being able to come here again is a win, don't you think？
Is that a jewelry museum？ I want to go there.
There's no time. There's a museum in Towano too. Let's go！
Oh, hey, hey. You can see the city from there！
There's the train station around there and the beach... Where's the hotel we're staying today？
I think it would be even better if we come here at night...
Ah, we have to go back to the hotel.
Yes. Hmmー, we went to a lot of places today.
Right. But it isn't over yet, right？
Two people can stay in this room.
Isn't it strange if two people stay together many times？
Strange...？ Why would it be strange？
Because... we're only high school students.
It doesn't matter. There's nothing wrong with it, right？
I have a reservation under the name ▲苗字▲...
Then, I will guide you to your room.
Please give me your luggage dear wife.
Emm... I- Me！？ Yes... Thank you very much.
Haha, I wonder if we look like a couple.
(She's bright red. I'm embarrassed too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Not that... I thought it was a separated room.
No, it's not available. I wonder if it was a mistake. I wonder what we should do.
I don't want to bother the hotel staff. I will stay in the same room.
I want to stay with you forever.
Yes, will we get used to it soon？
I wonder about that... But don't you feel like losing if you get used to it？ That's no fun.
Look, the sweets that are prepared beforehand. When you come to a room like this, why not check it？
Really？ Oh, let's have some tea.
Hey, let's go explore inside the hotel, ▲高嶺＊＊▲
Hehe, exploration？ It's okay... Ah, but...
While we explore, let's hold hands all the time.
Because some boys seem to easily get lost.
And because of that, I won't leave you alone. Shall we hold hands？
Hey, isn't your throat dry？ Should we buy some juice？
Hmm？ Ah, I'm okay. Thank you.
My throat is dry after all. I'll go buy some juice.
I see, I'm sorry. It's okay, I'll buy it. What would you like？
It's fine. I'll go, please wait for me, okay？
(I'm sure it's just my imagination. It's fine.)
(It's strange. I'm worried, so I'll go find her.)
I'm sorry, I'm a little late. I got lost.
(She went to the bathroom and bought some juice. I wonder why she doesn't use the one in the room.)
There's still time until dinner. We should take a bath first.
Ah, yes. A bath... that's right.
Huh？ This hotel seems to have various baths...
It seems that men and women change depending on the time.
Hmm... At this hour, Roman bath is for men and Flower bath is for women. Is that okay？
Yes, I want to take a flower bath.
...Yes. Say, can you wait outside for me before we go？
(Well, if you think carefully, there are some things you don't want to see...)
What is it？ You're looking too much...
Hey, when you finish your bath, can you wait here so we can go back together？
Yes, a little longing. Hehe, see you.
(We walked around quite a bit today, let's relax.)
(She isn't here yet. Well, that's okay. I'll wait for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(She's taking too long... I wonder why girl's take too much time to bathe.)
I'm sorry, I kept you waiting ▲主人公＊▲.
It's because you're wearing the same, right？
A yukata worn by a man is different from the one worn by a woman！
Hehe, it looks delicious. Ah, why don't you sit down？
Geez, it's bad manners to hurry. Bon appetit.
It was very delicious. Thanks for the meal.
Thank you very much. If you have finished, I will tell you something.
That's right, Dear customers. Have you heard the story of the legendary beach？
Yes, there is an island called Hatsushima that can be reached by boat from Atami Port.
In that place, there's a beach no one has reached.
And the legend says that if a couple swear their love can be happy forever.
If you act like a couple, you may find it.
Well then, I'll excuse myself. Take your time.
Tomorrow, we will absolutely going to find it.
(You're so happy, so it's okay, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I want to go there again.
Yes, it's a place we have memories.
That's right, let's go find it...
Hey, hey, there seems to be a table tennis over there, why don't we play？
It's a match, bring it ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Don't pull out now. It's a serious match between us, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Nice！ I won against you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
This is also the result of practice, although I haven't won at tennis yet...
Hah... my complete defeat, I sweated even after taking a bath.
Don't be depressed. When we get home, let's practice hard together！
(If you do your best, I won't win forever, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
It's a little troublesome, so let's pass.
That so. But it looks fun...
(Ah, there's an open-air bath. I would invite ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(I just went in, I don't need another bath.)
We should go take an outdoor bath, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
An outdoor bath. We should not. We just bathed.
I see... Then I won't go in.
An outdoor bath... That's right, let's go.
(It's covered with snow... it was falling without us realizing.)
Yes, I'm surprised！ It's beautiful, it was nice to come here.
Yes, it's beautiful！ It was nice to come here！
Should we stop talking like this？
Why？ Oh, did someone else come in here？
Not that, but... let's talk while taking a bath.
There seems to be a private bath here... Why don't we go together？
Really？ I'm glad. Then I'll go in first.
(A private bath is a family bath... I wonder what I should do.)
I should act like a man...
(This is the family bath. Where are you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
It's embarrassing, so don't look around too much, okay？
It's fun to wear a swimsuit in a hot spring. It's harder in a larger bath, because there are other people.
We've been together all the time, but I felt alone when taking a bath.
(I'm glad I'm wearing trunks... I was about to be treated as a pervert.)
Wah, people will hear us！ I understand, I'll be out！
(I wonder if you can understand me at all, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(That's right, I told her that the night view would be beautiful. I should tell ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(It's too dark, I should not say anything.)
Would you like to go for a night walk, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Today, when you looked over the city, you said it would be beautiful at night, right？
Yes... I want to go. It's already dark, should we risk it？
I see... That's right. I understand.
You remembered. Yes, I want to go. But, it's too late... Should we not？
It'll be okay, I will be there. Let's go.
It's like the princess being taken out of the castle... I'm kidding.
Haha. Then princess, lend me your hand.
It's a bit far, but I'll walk.
Thank you for listening to my selfish request.
It's not selfish. It was nice to be able to see it together.
Hey, there'll a fireworks display soon, ▲主人公＊▲.
I see. It's summer and we are close to the beach.
Would you like to go see them？
Yes, we couldn't see them without coming here.
Hey, the name of the sun beach changes at night ▲主人公＊▲.
It'll lit up and become a moonlight beach. Want to go？
It's really lit up... Isn't this black light？
The sea is shining blue. It's beautiful...
Let's go back to our room, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
(I see, I'm a little nervous too.)
Is it time to turn off the lights？
It's a waste going to sleep like this... I'm with you.
Well then, shall we turn in？
Isn't our futon a little too close？
Yes, it wasn't this close at first.
Good morning. Did you sleep well last night？
Good morning. Ah, it's quite early to get up.
...Huh？ I'm so sorry. It seems I got the time wrong.
(I'm glad I got up early. I slept really well yesterday.)
(Maybe I'll watch you for a while...)
That's cruel, tickling me while sleeping.
It's because you don't wake up easily.
I was feeling lonely, and I wanted to hug you.
I've been wanting to do this for a while...
Emm, I want to change my clothes.
Yes, you've finished. Let's go eat.
(It's okay because she had already finished.)
It's okay now. Thank you ▲主人公＊▲.
The breakfast inside a hotel is a buffet.
Alright, I'll eat both rice and bread！
Geez, do you want to break your stomach？
Haha, it's nothing. I'll also get a drink.
Alright, let's go. Let's get ready to leave.
Yes, I want to come again.
Today we go to Hatsushima. I wonder if we can find the legendary beach.
I wish we could go to our place of legends where we made nice memories.
It'll be alright, we'll find it.
It's a boat ride from here to Hatsushima.
It's exciting to get on a boat. Wanna get aboard now？
Hmm, so this is how it looks like from the inside？
(Isn't there something interesting to see around here...)
No, it's nothing like that... Do you know where the engines are？
Geez, I'm going to go outside, okay？
Oh, it's pretty fast. The wind feels good.
It was high time you come here.
Hey, when you stand in a place like this, you feel like imitating a movie.
That's not true. You look cute when doing it okay, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hehe, shall we do it together？
Ah, yes. What should I do？
Anyway, it looks like something a kid would do.
Yes, it's kind of a cute island.
Haha, it's a bit small. What should we do first？
Alright. Let's go eat something first.
Hey hey, should we eat here？
This also looks delicious. Can I eat it？
Now then, I wonder if we can find the legendary beach.
Oh, there is also a shrine.
Ah, there's also a legend on it.
I'm not going to go into detail here.
What kind of story is it？ Is it related to the legendary beach？
It would be nice if we could be sure.
Hatsushima Lighthouse... It's not that big, but I think is cute.
Normally, a lighthouse is along the coast. But this is in the middle, maybe because it's a small island.
It looks like you can climb up.
Oh, it's amazing. You can see all directions.
We come from Atami port over there. Ito is over there, and the Miura Peninsula and the Boso Peninsula！
You're right, it's written here. As expected of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Haha, I'm tired from traveling too.
I hope we can find the legendary beach no one knows.
I wonder if the legend is truly a legend.
Don't make that kind of sad face. I'm glad we came, even if we couldn't find the beach.
Can you hear that？ The sound of waves...
No, I can hear it. Over there！
Wait, I hear something... The same sound of waves from before.
Ah, it's true. I can also hear them.
I can't help it, it's a legend... But, I wanted to go again.
Look... Over there is the legendary beach...
Ah... It's not really on the map.
This beach is unknown to many people.
What we heard yesterday, about swearing our love...
I, Manaka Takane, vow to love you all my life.
I, ▲苗字▲ ▲名前▲, also pledge to love Manaka Takane for all my life.
Sometimes I remember what I was doing before.
I wonder what changed in me.
There are things that can make you nervous...
Being able to love someone... It's such a happy feeling.
Since then, my heart beats so fast...
Every time you tell me something...
I feel I love you more and more.
From now on, keep teaching me a lot of thing, okay？
From now on, we will always be together...
The beach... The legendary beach is around here.
Oh, it's true. It's not even on the map.
Do you remember the story from yesterday？
I, Makana Takane, vow to love you for the rest of my life.
I, ▲苗字▲ ▲名前▲も, also pledge to love Manaka Takane for all my life.
I was wondering if we truly would come here.
I didn't come with Papa and Mama.
I wonder if I can say anything.
But, I'm glad we could come...
Otherwise, we couldn't see this scenery.
We couldn't be together like this...
Just imagining it makes me sad.
That is why, I love you so much...
The legendary beach... The legendary beach is right here.
Amazing... we found it. It's beautiful...
I, Manaka Takane, vow to love you all my life.
I, ▲苗字▲ ▲名前▲, also pledge to love Makana Takane for all my life.
It's really beautiful. I'm glad we came...
We've been together for a long time...
I don't have to go home when I grow up.
I get more and more greedy.
Even if it changes a lot.
I can't do anything about this feeling...
It's the same as before... The place of our memories.
Because it's a legend. It might be our own private place.
I remember when we first arrived here.
The excitement of that time... and now...
...I don't know. Even now, I'm still nervous.
I can't do anything more than to think about it.
But I still love you, that will never change.
It's the same thing as before...
Hmmー. Our trip is almost over.
Are you tired？ Do you want something to drink？
There's still a little time left until the train arrives.
That's right, let's relax a little.
You're right. I wonder what I should buy...
Who are you buying it for？
Why are you giving gifts to everyone in school？
I mean, we would be in trouble if they ask...
You don't know that many people at school, right？
Yes. However, my neighbors and my parents' patients count as having many known people.
(I guess it's not something you have to worry about, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Did you get a sunburn, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes. When I took a bath, my skin was tingling.
I'm really tired. I wanna sleep.
Yes, me too... I'm gonna fall asleep soon.
Then, let's get some rest while we arrive.
No problem, your sleeping face is cute！
This familiar station... We're back to our everyday life.
It's the first time we've been together for so long.
That's right... Do you think we doubled the record？
I wonder what should we do to extend the record.
Just being like we are, after all.
Thank you for escorting me back.
Yes, then... this is the end of our trip.
Before we say goodbye, don't you forget this, okay？
(Going back home alone after the trip is kinda sad.)
Sorry. I have no special reason for this, but... I just don't want to leave yet.
You just have to be here for a little bit, and then I'll go back home.
It's okay. But don't do it that way, okay？ It's dangerous.
Because we are newlyweds, isn't kissing normal？
We are newlyweds Isn't kissing normal？
(You can only see her like this here.)
I'm glad to be with you...
Ah, hey. Can you see it？
Can we take a photo later？ Hehe.
I wonder if there is a delicious restaurant somewhere.
Ah. Hey, can we stop by that shop？
It's a good day for a walk, right？
We're going to get sunburned. I wonder if that's okay.
I would like to eat local ice cream▼
Momiji, maybe I'll bring one to commemorate. Hehe.
Look, the autumn leaves over there are beautiful, right？
It's because we're together we aren't cold, right？
Ah, I want to drink something warm.
From here, I wonder what kind of scenery we can see.
There's a game... Do you want to play？ Hehe！
Seems like there are many things around, shall we look？
I wonder if we can see the sea from here.
I want to be with you for a while longer...
Emm... don't look around too much, okay...？
Hey, what do you want to do next？
Are you tired？ Are you all right？
Look, we have a great view, right？
Hehe. Then, yes. Here you go.
Geez... Want to have it early？
Thank you！ Can I open it？
No, it's embarrassing. Keep it closed.
Hmm, well said. I'm kidding... Take your time at home, okay？
Of course！ Yay！ Thank you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
It's nothing. I'm glad it made you so happy.
I'm glad I did my best... Hehe.
What day is it？ Oh... February 14th！
Ah, today's my birthday. Thank you！
Hehe, geez... Don't you forget that until my birthday, okay？
And then, here is your present. Can you accept it？
You're welcome. It can be returned, so please feel free to return it at any time.
Return something you give me？ Never. Even if heaven and earth are destroyed, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Geez, how can you make those things sound so nice？
Hehe, but I'm glad you're so happy. Happy Birthday.
Yes. Today is your birthday, isn't it？ So, here it is...
You're welcome. Tell me if you don't like it, okay？ You can return it.
I won't return a gift if it's from you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
How can you say that before looking at it？
Hehe. I'm happy you say that.
Well then, once more. Happy birthday. Let's have a nice year together, right？
Did you forget your birthday？ Well... then I won't give you this.
Wait a minute！ I do！ Give me my present！
Hehehe！ Can you promise me something？ Don't forget my birthday！
What's with that？ Hehe, but I forgive you.
It's a wonderful day when you were born, right？ Here you go.
Yes. Happy birthday. I hope we have a great year.
Happy birthday！ I want to give this to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah... Thank you！ Hey, can I open it？
Ah, Ah... This is what I wanted！ Thank you so much.
Yes, this is nice. Thank you.
(She doesn't seem to like it much...)
Did it take time to choose this？
Hehe. You worked hard and thought about me, thank you. I'll cherish it, okay？
If you ask me, I have little choice.
Hehe！ Surely there are couples around the world having this kind of conversation, right？
It was nice being together. Let's keep getting along, okay？
Isn't today your birthday？ Here, a gift for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
